    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Effect</strong>: You gain the following benefits: </p><ul><li><p><em>Royal Authority:</em> </p><p>Inhabitants of your nation must obey your lawful orders or suffer the consequences. </p></li><li><p><em>Royal Majesty:</em> </p><p>Your choice of your Might or Presence increases by 1 (to a maximum of 6). </p></li></ul><p>Additionally, choose one of the following benefits: </p><ul><li><p><em>Crown Jewels:</em> </p><p>You gain one of your nation’s treasures—a trinket of the Director’s choice. </p></li><li><p><em>Royal Fame:</em> </p><p>You earn 2 Renown. </p></li><li><p><em>Royal Retinue:</em> </p><p>The number of followers you can recruit increases by 2. </p></li><li><p><em>Royal Wealth:</em> </p><p>You earn 2 Wealth. </p></li></ul><p><strong>Special</strong>: If you take this title, you might be called upon to perform duties for your nation.</p>",
